**Scapegoat** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The **scapegoat** believes themself to be a civilian. The first time the **scapegoat** would die from a *basic attack*, they will survive. The attacker will learn the **scapegoat**'s role, and the next time the attacker would be lynched, the **scapegoat** is lynched in their place.

__Formalized__
Identity: Civilian
Starting: Process: Protect @Self from `Attacks` through Partial Defense (~Permanent)
On Partial Defense:
  • Process:
    ‣ Reveal `@Self is a **Scapegoat**` to @AttackLocation
    ‣ Apply `ScapegoatDefense` to @Attacker (~Persistent)
